('Dr. A.K.M. Ashikur Rahman', 'ashikurrahman', 'Professor', '880 2 9665650, Extension 7959', '880 2 9665650, Extension 6498', '01556329138 (Serious calls plz', 'ashikur AT cse DOT buet DOT ac DOT bd, (help me in avoiding spam!)', 'Department of Computer Science and Engineering (CSE)<br> Bangladesh University of Engineering and Technology (BUET)Dhaka-1000, Bangladesh', 'http://teacher.buet.ac.bd/ashikur', '  <li><b>Wireless Ad hoc and Sensor Networks</b> </li>\r\n  <ul>\r\n    <li><i>Routing</i>:The path problem and relavent optimisation criteria. </li>\r\n    <ul>\r\n        <li>Location-based routing, Power-aware routing, QoS routing.</li>\r\n    </ul>\r\n    <li><i> Medium Access Control Layer Issues:</i> Enhancing reliability, </li>\r\n    <ul>\r\n        <li> Reliable unicast, multicast and broadcast transmission,\r\nCollision avoidance. </li>\r\n    </ul>\r\n    <li> <i>Power Optimisation:</i> Topology control for energy-efficiency.</li>\r\n    <li><i>Capacity Analysis:</i> Performance bounds and Capacity limit.</li>\r\n  </ul>\r\n  <li><b>Back-end optimisation of Compiler</b><br>\r\n  </li>\r\n  <ul>\r\n    <li><i>Loop optimisation</i>: Loop Fusion and Fission, scalar optimization,\r\nalias analysis.</li>\r\n  </ul>\r\n  <li><b>Neural Network</b><br>\r\n  </li>\r\n  <ul>\r\n    <li>Image compression </li>\r\n  </ul>\r\n  <li><b>Thin Client Architecture</b></li>\r\n  <ul>\r\n    <li>Optimising thin clients</li>\r\n    <li>Thin clients on small wireless devices</li>\r\n    <li>Server-Based Computing<br>\r\n    </li>\r\n  </ul>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <ul>\r\n    <ul> \r\n    </ul> \r\n  </ul>\r\n<br>\r\n<b><font color="#FF00FF" size="2">\r\nIF YOU CANNOT DO GREAT THINGS, DO SMALL THINGS IN A GREAT WAY</font></b>\r\n<p>\r\n<br>\r\n<b><font color="#FF00FF" size="2">\r\nTHE ONLY TIME "SUCCESS" COMES BEFORE "WORK" IS IN THE DICTIONARY.</font></b>\r\n<p>\r\n<br>\r\n<b><font color="#FF00FF" size="2">\r\n&#2474;&#2499;&#2469;&#2495;&#2476;&#2496;&#2468;&#2503; &#2453;&#2